# KayTech Africa — Google favicon / logo (this project only)

Goal: Google Search shows the **KayTech logo** from `public/logo.jpg`, not a Vercel/v0 default icon.

## This repo only

These rules apply to **kaytech-africa** only. Other projects use their own branding.

## Favicon source of truth

- Generate from `public/logo.jpg`: `npm run brand-assets` (runs on build)
- Files: `public/favicon.ico`, `public/icon-192.png`, `public/icon-512.png`, `src/app/favicon.ico`
- Do **not** restore default Next/Vercel triangle favicons

## HTML head

`src/app/layout.tsx` must include:

```html
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" sizes="48x48" />
```

Square icons, 48×48 or multiples (96, 192, 512). Organization JSON-LD logo should point at `/icon-512.png`.

## What Google needs (not code alone)

1. Production URL indexed: `https://www.kaytechafrica.com` (Search Console → Request indexing)
2. Favicon crawlable: `/favicon.ico` returns 200 on **www**, not only `*.vercel.app`
3. **Weeks** for Google to refresh favicons after deploy — not instant

Google does not guarantee favicons in results even when configured correctly.
